description.narrative: By 2025, UNICEF Staff and partners have mechanisms in place to deliver quality social and behavioural change interventions, which contributes to Cross-Sectoral Communication For Development, Cross-Sectoral Communication For Development (Covid), Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2025, UNICEF Somalia staff and partners have enhanced capacity to design, implement and monitor programmes, and as well as generate evidence through research and evaluations
